Rotavirus vaccination was selected to illustrate the working of the previous model construct. A Belgium hospital (Jessa Hospital) was chosen as the vaccine was introduced in Belgium in 2006. The perspective considered is the healthcare payer. Table 1 summarizes the data inputs.


